Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:34.43,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眩しい風のなかで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:37.52,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描くよ　君の笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:43.31,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}素直になれる瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:46.73,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}小さなことで揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:50.33,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}弱い自分が悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:54.12,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泣きたいときだって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:56.24,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}上を向いて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:01:01.92,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}わたしだけにできることがあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:10.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あきらめないよ　君を守り続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:16.53,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}とまらないスピードで想いがあふれていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:18.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}負けたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:22.78,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰よりも輝いていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:25.71,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}星がみえない日も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:28.85,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}光はある　きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:31.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}信じること…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:34.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}願い、　未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:42.18,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの空で逢えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================opcn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:34.43,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}炫目的风中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:37.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}描绘你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:43.31,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}变得坦率的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:46.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因小事而动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:50.33,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}软弱的自己令我懊恼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:54.12,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:56.24,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也仰头忍泪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:01:01.92,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}必定有唯有我能做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:10.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}永不言弃 一直守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:16.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思念正以停不下的速度膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:18.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不想认输
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.78,0:01:22.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}愿比任何人都耀目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:25.71,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使夜空没有繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:28.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}亦会有光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:31.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:34.97,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}前往未来的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:42.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}能在那片天空相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================zhengwen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只奏效一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后果怎样 我可不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是用着跟千冬姐一样的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是无人机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没有备过案的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,0)\bord2\blur4\pos(455,35)\fs26\1c&HE4E4E4&\3c&H2D2D2D&}Boy Meets Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除你之外 全都是女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计碰到不少好事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少扯谎了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是看你的短信 都觉得你身处乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没招待券
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啦 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还好 铃转学过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟能聊天的对象少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～铃啊 铃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥 午饭好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.33,0:02:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧下楼吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 一夏哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 兰啊 好久不见 打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天刚好外出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家看看情况 顺便就过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰 你好歹也敲个门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家会以为你是不知羞耻的女…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没告诉你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 一夏哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你慢吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换了身衣服啊 是不是要出去?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 约会?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在学校也这样子是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃也够惨的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要搬家了～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间调整安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱之之要搬去其他房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请 请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是必须马上搬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总不能老让年轻男女住同一间房嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且筱之之也住得不舒适吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不在了 也能按时起床刷牙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 我马上搬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧 反正想也没结果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 忘记拿东西了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛这么一本正经啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个月的各学年个人竞技赛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 要是我拿了冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 就跟我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大新闻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听说「那个」没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 前段时间的IS么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是实验中的机体失控了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 这个月的竞技赛拿冠军的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以跟织斑交往哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么大家说得那么起劲 在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这误传的 还一传十 十传百了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不是又胡说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自认为是没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:42.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐到位置上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开班会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要向大家介绍一位插班生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫夏尔鲁·迪诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是法国过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男 男生?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 听说这里有跟我同样情况的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从祖国转过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生 第二个男生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还在我们班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅哥 而且还是激发人保护欲的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵 安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天跟二班一起进行IS实习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自马上换衣服 到第二操场集合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 织斑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你负责照顾迪诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是男生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是织斑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好好 我们先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生要换衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到竞技场的更衣室换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次实习都要到那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要早点适应哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 看你心神不宁的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上厕所?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 发现传说中的插班生了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还跟织斑在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐妹们 出来看帅哥呐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 他俩还牵着手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织斑的黑发是很不错 金发也很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 至少先拍张照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家这么激动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为目前能操纵IS的男性只有我俩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算甩掉她们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 刚来就给你添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客气啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你来了真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个男的在这学校 可痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后多关照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫织斑一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就叫一夏好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 多关照 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以叫我夏尔鲁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抓紧就迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班主任对时间要求很严的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这就换
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 请转过身去 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 也没打算盯着你换衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都行了 抓紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你换得超快的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这衣服 光着身子时挺难穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总卡着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡着?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这套似乎挺容易穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是迪诺亚公司制作的版本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪诺亚?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也姓迪诺亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸是社长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是法国最大的IS相关企业了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 社长少爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 难怪什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 怎么说呢 气质方面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出是受过良好家教的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才说难怪嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起 我们开始实习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先进行战斗演习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凰 奥鲁戈多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专用机拥有者能马上开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上前来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉这样像秀给人看一样 真不是滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们拿点干劲出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能展示优点给那家伙看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在果然是本英国代表候补生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉亚·奥鲁戈多上场的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个展示专用机拥有者的实力差距的好机会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才老师说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那对手是?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟铃打一场也没所谓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 这才是我要说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心被干翻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别急 蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的对手是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…织斑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很为难的～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过顺着这条线发展下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织斑老师就当我大姑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也很有吸引力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜啊 射偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织斑 没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田老师是原代表候补
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那样的射击是易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是过去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也仅仅止步于候补生了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 小姑娘们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 是二对一吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也实在…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们现在这水平 很快就会输
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会留手的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那下我可没认真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来解说一下山田老师操纵的IS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田老师的IS 是迪诺亚公司制作的「Rafale Revive」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是第二世代开发最后期的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的规格并不逊色于初期第三世代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是目前所配备的量产IS中最后兴起的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有世界第三的市场份额
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据不同装备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格斗 射击 防御全部型号都能切换
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到本小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 干嘛全被她看穿了要往哪儿躲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要怪你呢 让你乱射冲击炮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下各位都领教到教职员的实力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后记得带着敬意跟她们打交道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 分组实习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组长由专用机拥有者担任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 马上分组
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织斑 一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂的地方要教我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看看迪诺亚的操纵技术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以在这组吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便到处摸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了伤我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位按顺序装着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时 精英的身份真让我痛恨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 就按学号来进行IS的装着 启动和步行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学号1 相川清香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手球部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴趣是观看体育比赛和慢跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从第一印象就决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他接下来也够呛的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 不错不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那试着停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就换下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼 好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.75,0:15:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我够不着驾驶位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 最开始常见的失败呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织斑 麻烦帮她坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织斑 叫出白式吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么弄我上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是抱上去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱到驾驶位那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抱我…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意别滑下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中的…公主抱吗～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道怎么坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那启动和步行之后就换人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天中午有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那偶而也一起吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就这么定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起更美味嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且夏尔鲁才刚转学过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还摸不清东南西北吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话是没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我跟着真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客气啥 都是爷们儿 搞好关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天起 咱俩还住一房
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 一夏真是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害羞啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是咕噜肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 今天早上做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说了想吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 碰巧我今天偶尔也早醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就做了这些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得让你认可英国也有好东西吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 看样子还真不像吹的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先吃这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 可以尽情放开吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 我等下再吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 接下来是帚的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,样样看起来都很花心思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只 只是顺便罢了 顺便
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是花时间做给自己吃罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是也很开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦 帚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.10,0:18:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很费功夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用姜 酱油和蒜蓉调味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还事先掺了点胡椒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加了适量的萝卜泥当调料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帚 你不吃真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败作 我全吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你说好吃就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也吃点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 尝一块
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那我就不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 这炸鸡真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是炸鸡…不过好吃就是好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 这是不是在日本 情侣间会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「来 啊～」的情景?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们关系真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥是他俩关系好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 我要求重来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如大家一点点地交换便当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相喂食的话就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然一夏觉得没问题 我也OK
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本我是不会仿这种有损餐桌礼仪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.95,0:20:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过入乡要随俗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就赶紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 吃咕噜肉吧 咕噜肉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一夏 尝尝这三文治
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是爷们儿真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟红茶很不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你放学后总是进行IS的特训
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 毕竟我落后于其他同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能也加入
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有专用机 应该能帮到你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也有个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上又来一位新朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.84,0:21:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是从德国过来的插班生 拉乌拉·博迪薇希
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然连续两天有插班生过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家安静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家还没自我介绍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打个招呼吧 拉乌拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 教官
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教官?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是千冬姐在德国时的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉乌拉·博迪薇希
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然是她的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.31,0:22:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不认同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说又有插班生了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.25,0:23:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这次是德国的代表候补生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.58,0:23:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎跟织斑有非一般的因缘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.50,0:23:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她会这么敌视织斑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:23:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有她跟千冬大人的关系是?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谜团不断增多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.09,0:23:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底过去 发 发生了什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.85,0:24:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 迪诺亚那边似乎也会有点剧情发展哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 室友是金发贵公子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(407,325)\fs16}（Gentle）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.29,0:24:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美少年的秘密 终于要浮出水面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===============================zhengwen2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.05,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.10,zhengwen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织斑 快教我们IS的操纵法吧
